[{"text": "代號：3103", "conf": 0.9992316365242004, "xmin": 2086.0, "xmax": 2377.0, "ymin": 73.0, "ymax": 135.0, "cx": 2231.5, "cy": 103.75}, {"text": "頁次：10-9", "conf": 0.9990943074226379, "xmin": 2091.0, "xmax": 2389.0, "ymin": 125.0, "ymax": 190.0, "cx": 2240.0, "cy": 157.5}, {"text": "68", "conf": 0.9999027252197266, "xmin": 48.0, "xmax": 121.0, "ymin": 204.0, "ymax": 258.0, "cx": 84.5, "cy": 231.0}, {"text": "依《本草備要》，肉桂下列敘述何者錯誤？", "conf": 0.9821406006813049, "xmin": 176.0, "xmax": 1146.0, "ymin": 201.0, "ymax": 275.0, "cx": 661.0, "cy": 238.0}, {"text": "(A)辛苦大熱，氣厚純陽。治痼冷沉寒", "conf": 0.9881637096405029, "xmin": 180.0, "xmax": 1005.0, "ymin": 270.0, "ymax": 336.0, "cx": 592.5, "cy": 303.0}, {"text": "(B)補命門相火之衰，益陽消陰", "conf": 0.9993536472320557, "xmin": 180.0, "xmax": 854.0, "ymin": 338.0, "ymax": 402.0, "cx": 516.75, "cy": 370.0}, {"text": "(C)疏通血脈，宣導百藥，去營衛風寒", "conf": 0.9981589913368225, "xmin": 177.0, "xmax": 1002.0, "ymin": 406.0, "ymax": 467.0, "cx": 589.5, "cy": 436.25}, {"text": "(D)治欻逆結氣之藥理，欻逆亦由氣不歸元，桂能引火歸宿丹田", "conf": 0.9695137143135071, "xmin": 175.0, "xmax": 1555.0, "ymin": 469.0, "ymax": 528.0, "cx": 865.0, "cy": 498.5}, {"text": "69", "conf": 0.9999369978904724, "xmin": 35.0, "xmax": 111.0, "ymin": 533.0, "ymax": 590.0, "cx": 73.0, "cy": 561.5}, {"text": "下列何藥物不具益腎助陽、固精，縮尿的功效？", "conf": 0.9813922047615051, "xmin": 174.0, "xmax": 1242.0, "ymin": 535.0, "ymax": 592.0, "cx": 708.0, "cy": 563.5}, {"text": "(A)桑螵蛸", "conf": 0.9535837769508362, "xmin": 169.0, "xmax": 392.0, "ymin": 599.0, "ymax": 664.0, "cx": 280.5, "cy": 631.5}, {"text": "(C)金櫻子", "conf": 0.9824810028076172, "xmin": 1293.0, "xmax": 1499.0, "ymin": 597.0, "ymax": 652.0, "cx": 1396.25, "cy": 624.5}, {"text": "(D)山藥", "conf": 0.8999391794204712, "xmin": 1840.0, "xmax": 2004.0, "ymin": 592.0, "ymax": 653.0, "cx": 1922.0, "cy": 622.5}, {"text": "(B)覆盆子", "conf": 0.981722891330719, "xmin": 735.0, "xmax": 947.0, "ymin": 598.0, "ymax": 659.0, "cx": 841.0, "cy": 628.5}, {"text": "70", "conf": 0.999902